s at the Democratic and Republican National Conventions and offered analysis and strategic recommendations. <I>Smart</I>Meme trainers have also worked at the SPIN academy, offering support and skills training for interfacing with the media. <BR>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</P></FONT>','','2005-04-12 07:32:50',15,1,1,'',0,'',1,'',7,0,'','pdf',0,1,'',0,'','0000-00-00',0,0,0,0,'PRIMETIME4.jpg','<i>Smart</i>Meme conducted a survey of organizations mobilizing for the 2004 DNC and RNC and collected nearly 100 responses. The results are explored and analysed in this 26- page report that was published online in July 2004.',1,'',0,0,'','','left','',0,'pic','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'','',1,1,0,'','','','','',NULL,NULL,NULL),(941,199,'INCITE/INSIGHT:\r\nStory Telling, Movement Building, and Creating a Culture of Strategy...\r\n','September 29-October 3,  2005\r\nAndover, New Hampshire','The first gathering convened by smartMeme\'s new STORY program  (Strategy,\r\nTraining, and Organizing Resources for Youth) focused on power analysis,\r\nstory telling and movement building.\r\n\r\nIn a rural retreat setting, we will take 3 1/2 days to explore narrative power analysis,\r\nstory-based strategies, creative direct action at the point(s) of assumption and more!\r\n\r\nIncite/Insight will be a unique and intimate gathering of young activists\r\n(18 - 30 years old) working for systemic social change.  The conference will\r\noffer a reflective forum for deep discussions on the system, our strategies,\r\nmovement building, and how the stories we tell can reshape our world.\r\n\r\nSessions will focus on the power of story, the landscape of media,\r\nleadership and organization, and points of intervention to change the story\r\nfor a more hopeful future.\r\n\r\nMORE INFORMATION COMING SOON at www.smartMeme.com\r\n\r\n** SAVE THE DATE ** SAVE THE DATE**\r\n\r\nSeptember 29-October 3,  2005\r\n','','2005-07-16 01:13:09',63,1,1,'',0,'',0,'',0,0,'','',0,1,'',0,'The first gathering convened by sma