le;\">Incite/Insight is the first gathering convened by <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">smart</span>Meme\'s new STORY program (Strategy, Training, and Organizing Resources for Youth) and will focus on power analysis, story telling and movement building. The retreat will facilitate STORY’s work to build a culture of strategy in grassroots youth movements by gathering youth leaders from diverse networks for a deep think about movement building and the power of story. <br /><br />In a rural retreat setting, we will take three days to explore narrative power analysis, story-based strategies, creative direct action at the point(s) of assumption, and more! <br /><br />Incite/Insight will be a unique and intimate gathering of young activists <br />(18 - 30 years old) working for systemic social change.  The conference will <br />offer a reflective forum for deep discussions on the system(s), our strategies, <br />movement building, and how the stories we tell can reshape our world.<br /><br />For more information about STORY <a href=\"http://smartmeme.com/article.php?list=type&type=50\">click here</a> (with link to new about STORY page)<br /><br />For more information about <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">smart</span>Meme <a href=\"http://smartmeme.com/article.php?list=type&type=4\">click here</a> (with link to “what we do”)<br /></body></html>','','2005-07-22 12:47:47',1,1,1,'',0,'',1,'',0,0,'','',0,8,'',0,'','0000-00-00',0,0,0,0,'','',0,'',0,3,'','','','',0,'','2005-07-22 00:00:00',0,'','',1,1,0,'','','','','',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1013,213,'Incite/Insight','A youth-based strategy skill share convened by <i>smart</i>Meme’s STORY Program (Strategy, Training, and Organizing Resources for Youth)','\r\n<html><head></head><body style=\"visibility: visible;\">Incite/Insight is the first gathering convened by <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">smart</span>Meme\'s new STORY program (Strategy, Training, and Organizing Resources for Youth) and will focus on power analysis, sto