ver process your organization or coalition utilizes or help you find the decision making structure that is right for your situation.\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Research, Analysis &amp; Conducting Strategic Think Tanks</b> <br />\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<i>Smart</i>Meme’s collective maintains an extensive library of advocacy, media, and issue reference material. As veteran researchers we can provide research and analysis support for any project you’re undertaking, from academic to action based.  <i>Smart</i>Meme can also conduct group strategic sessions (think tanks) where we facilitate a one-day or multi-day discussion on an emerging or current issue and/or campaign. These think tank sessions can be combined with one or more of our many  <a href=\"article.php?list=type&type=50\">trainings</a>, to help catalyze new approaches to  critical issues and campaign work.\r\n<br />\r\n</font></p></body></html>','','2005-07-25 20:04:39',34,0,1,'',0,'',1,'',0,0,'','',0,8,'',0,'','2005-07-25',1,0,0,0,'','',0,'',0,0,'','','','',0,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'','',1,1,0,'','','','','',NULL,NULL,NULL),(1113,114,'communications','The right message at the right time to the right audience can make all the difference in your campaign.  <i>Smart</i>Meme will help you figure out what, how and when to get your campaign’s message out to the world.  ','\r\n<html><head></head><body><p align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"Times New Roman\" color=\"#000000\"><b>Comprehensive Strategic Communications Plan</b><br />  \r\n<i>Smart</i>Meme will work with you to develop your campaign’s overall strategic communications plan potentially including (1) marketing strategy (or organizational outreach/marketing strategy), (2) messaging, (3) media planning, (4) and campaign identity development (or organizational branding) plus logo design (see separate descriptions below). \r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<br />\r\n\r\n<b>Developing Marketing Strategy </b><br />\r\n\r\n<i>Smart</i>Meme can help you devel