ing of a long-term peace movement that can challenge the assumptions underlying racism, militarism and war.<br><br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Your Support</b><br><br>\r\n\r\nIf you want to offer solidarity and support to the youth and Veterans who are offering us new stories and new visions of what an antiwar movement in the US could look like, please make the most generous contribution you can. Your charitable gift can help to bring young Iraq Vets who are speaking out against the war, and young visionaries of the next generation of antiwar activism, together at Highlander to share stories and develop strategies to end the Iraq occupation and challenge US Empire. <br><br>\r\n\r\nNo one at the White House is going to end this war for us. It is up to us to dare to be more creative, strategic, and powerful! The STORY Collaborative will create a space for young leaders and young veterans to connect, find voice, and develop a collaborative vision. Be a part of this historic gathering and <a href=\"https://secure.groundspring.org/dn/index.php?aid=9879\">chose to make a gift of solidarity today.</a><br>  <br>\r\n\r\nFor Peace, <br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\nThe STORY Collaborative to End the War in Iraq','','2006-05-06 00:40:33',69,1,1,'',0,'',1,'',0,0,'Youth+VetsSTORYAppeal2006.pdf','pdf',0,8,'',0,'','2005-07-25',1,0,0,0,'young_vets.jpg','Young Iraq Veterans, Students, Counter Recruiters, and Peace Movement Builders Will Gather at Highlander July 7-10 2006',1,'',0,0,'','','right','',0,'pic','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'','',1,1,0,'','','','','','',NULL,NULL),(1214,213,'Incite/Insight: Story-Telling, Movement Building, and Creating a Culture of Strategy','A youth-based strategy skill share convened by <i>smart</i>Meme’s STORY Program (Strategy, Training, and Organizing Resources for Youth)\r\n\r\n*Important: if you have applied and have not received a confirmation email please email story@smartmeme.com.','\r\n \r\n                <p><strong>We are no longer taking applications for Incite/Insight.  Thank you to all that applied.  We have had an overwhelming repsonse and you will be notified by August 31st if you are accepted.  If you have a late application or any questions please email <a href=\"mailto:story@smartmeme.com\">story@smartmeme.com.</a>  </strong><br /></p><p> <br />Incite/Insight is the first gathering convened by <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">smart</span>Meme\'s new STORY program (Strategy, Training, and Organizing Resources for Youth) and will focus on power analysis, story telling and movement building. The retreat will facilitate STORY’s work to build a culture of strategy in grassroots youth movements by gathering youth leaders from diverse networks for a deep think about movement building and the power of story. <br /><br />In a rural retreat setting, we will take three days to explore narrative power analysis, story-based strategies, creative direct action at the point(s) of assumption, and more! <br /><br />Incite/Insight will be a unique and intimate gathering of young activists (18 - 30 years old) working for systemic social change. The conference will offer a reflective forum for deep discussions on the system(s), our strategies, movement building, and how the stories we tell can reshape our world.<br /><br />For more information about STORY <a href=\"http://smartmeme.com/article.php?list=type&amp;type=50\">click here</a><br /><br />For more information about <span style=\"font-style: italic;\">smart</span>Meme <a href=\"http://smartmeme.com/article.php?list=type&amp;type=4\">click here</a></p>','','2005-08-28 22:46:09',70,1,1,'about incite/insight',0,'',1,'',0,0,'','',0,8,'',0,'','2005-07-25',1,0,0,0,'bradley2_JPG_jpg_jpg.jpg','Join us for reflections on story telling, movement building, and creating a culture of strategy.',1,'',0,0,'','','right','',0,'pic','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,'','',1,1,0,'','','','','','',NULL,NULL),(1215,213,'The STORY Collaborative to End the War in Iraq','A youth-based strategy session convened by <i>sma