youth-based antiwar networks<br>\r\n•	Provide a space for building relationships across constituencies<br>\r\n•	Facilitate anti-war strategy development using story-based strategy models<br>\r\n•	Amplify the voices of youth and young veterans in the anti-war movement and build leadership capacity amongst these constituencies<br>\r\n•	Encourage the building of a long-term peace movement that can challenge the assumptions underlying racism, militarism and war.<br><br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Your Support</b><br><br>\r\n\r\nIf you want to offer solidarity and support to the youth and Veterans who are offering us new stories and new visions of what an antiwar movement in the US could look like, please make the most generous contribution you can. Your charitable gift can help to bring young Iraq Vets who are speaking out against the war, and young visionaries of the next generation of antiwar activism, together at Highlander to share stories and develop strategies to end the Iraq occupation and challenge US Empire. <br><br>\r\n\r\nNo one at the White House is going to end this war for us. It is up to us to dare to be more creative, strategic, and powerful! The STORY Collaborative will create a space for young leaders and young veterans to connect, find voice, and develop a collaborative vision. Be a part of this historic gathering and <a href=\"https://secure.groundspring.org/dn/index.php?aid=9879\">chose to make a gift of solidarity today.</a><br>  <br>\r\n\r\nFor Peace, <br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\nThe STORY Collaborative to End the War in Iraq','','2006-08-10 00:44:57',69,1,1,'',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,0,0,'Youth+VetsSTORYAppeal2006.pdf','pdf',NULL,8,'',0,'','2005-07-25',1,0,0,0,'young_vets.jpg','Young Iraq Veterans, Students, Counter Recruiters, and Peace Movement Builders Will Gather at Highlander July 7-10 2006',1,'',0,1,'','','right','',0,'pic','0000-00-00 00:00:00',1,'','',1,1,0,'','','','','','',NULL,NULL),(1228,214,'The STORY Collaborative to End the War in Iraq','An intimate 3-day retr